[[File:20011-08 przystanek woodstock 0 36.jpg|thumb|Polish youth in modern outfits attending a rock music festival, 2011]] [[Image:LA2-NSRW-2-0065.jpg|thumb|150px|right|Overview of fashion from ''The New Student's Reference Work'', 1914.]] [[Image:1794-1887-Fashion-overview-Alfred-Roller.GIF|thumb|150px|right|Summary of women's fashion silhouette changes 1794-1887]]
The '''history of Western fashion''' is the story of the changing [[fashion]]s in [[clothing]] for men and women in Europe and other countries under influence of the [[Western world]], from the 12th century to the present.
